{"tid":1125533,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"分離焦慮","createTime":"2019-04-25T18:41:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-26T01:55:25.000Z","uid":182195,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"92126ab80041fb78705f606c6287d70ae13576d9","tid":1125533,"uid":182195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T18:41:32.000Z","msg":"當另一半消失不見時會覺得好唔開心<br />\n擔心到心跳好快 想喊<br />\n有時佢唔出聲或者覆得慢都會咁<br />\n點處理<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47b14a57b5e3f0c4de1fc8a11d4172028c4495b5","tid":1125533,"uid":250517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"92126ab80041fb78705f606c6287d70ae13576d9","tid":1125533,"uid":182195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T18:41:32.000Z","msg":"當另一半消失不見時會覺得好唔開心<br />\n擔心到心跳好快 想喊<br />\n有時佢唔出聲或者覆得慢都會咁<br />\n點處理<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T18:50:13.000Z","msg":"做下其他野，分心"},{"pid":"d2bd1f71bfb0419efce70ebfd20a7c455a328a36","tid":1125533,"uid":158899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T19:03:31.000Z","msg":"你已沉船"},{"pid":"88e8c90baa85027c22f68568c573d440e88daf8a","tid":1125533,"uid":182195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d2bd1f71bfb0419efce70ebfd20a7c455a328a36","tid":1125533,"uid":158899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T19:03:31.000Z","msg":"你已沉船"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T19:14:17.000Z","msg":"好似中咗..."},{"pid":"e65a1dabeed7f538ce4506d620c3bb5778f3d078","tid":1125533,"uid":72226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T19:24:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />垃圾"},{"pid":"1b80e9dd52c9a47890e9ddb6c7cb01a3f6a85f68","tid":1125533,"uid":95499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T19:52:58.000Z","msg":"抄心經"},{"pid":"af29d0c21e2cf1808232fc8f9a1ae7d442db534e","tid":1125533,"uid":182195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e65a1dabeed7f538ce4506d620c3bb5778f3d078","tid":1125533,"uid":72226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T19:24:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />垃圾"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T19:56:00.000Z","msg":"比啲意見"},{"pid":"51d2a441ffc2206cf634a07ce6c9a11b4213e37c","tid":1125533,"uid":105102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T00:00:36.000Z","msg":"留名學嘢"},{"pid":"337f447d91575344f996e9aa1fa1660ad96365bc","tid":1125533,"uid":182195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T01:55:25.000Z","msg":"分離焦慮好多時都係源於小時候與家人嘅關係，多數係矛盾型依戀（insecurely attached：ambivalent），呢個係心理學嘅term，同路人可以睇下係咪啱<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>矛盾型依戀（insecurely attached：ambivalent）</strong><br />\n<br />\n當母親在身邊時，他們緊緊依偎在母親旁，寸步不離。當母親離開時，他們會哭鬧不已。當母親再回來時，他們會一邊親近，尋求安慰，另一方面又會對母親「拳打腳踢」。<br />\n<br />\n矛盾型依戀的孩童最易於長大後產生成人的分離焦慮。他們可能會以用嚎啕大哭、吵鬧等阻止對方離開；失敗的話會情緒低落，又會嘗試與對方疏離，好讓自己別太傷心；要是對方仍不回來的話，他們會嘗試接受分離，正常生活，但想到對方時仍會傷心。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>如何克服成人焦慮症？<br />\n</strong><br />\n患者保持活躍和忙碌，這樣當主要依賴的人離開時，讓頭腦會被其他事情所佔據；<br />\n開始寫日記，以更好的識別自身的情感，學會感受進入自己的模式；<br />\n患者要明白自己比其他人感情更敏感，患者愈是質疑對方的愛，對方就愈可能離患者而去。<br />\n保持積極的態度和外觀。當孤獨時，也要努力發現生活美好的一面。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n更多資料：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/article/183479\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2Farticle%2F183479&d=fAF%2FER2cs4qp%2F6NYk0BreByAur%2Bbp9MVyOkMM5%2FMxDY%3D&h=226c149b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/article/183479</a>"}]}